Description: This dataset contains the results of a quality assessment focused on the accessibility of IRIs contained in the DBpedia resources about persons and places. This assessment was performed using the [LD Sniffer](https://github.com/nandana/ld-sniffer) tool. The information about the evaluation process- metrics used- and results are described using the [Linked Data Quality Model](http://www.linkeddata.es/ontology/ldq#).
